  <div id="text-content_91902200-0E66-0135-CBA8-22000BC102FE" class="text-block-content">
    <p>You can record or upload video and audio files as part of your Inbox messages. </p>
<p>For more information about supported uploaded media types, please see the <a href="/t5/Student-Guide/What-types-of-media-files-can-I-upload-in-Canvas-as-a-student/ta-p/528" target="_blank">Canvas Media Files lesson</a>.</p>
<p><strong>Note: </strong>Attachments appear in your user files in the Conversation Attachments folder and count against the files limit for your account. </p>
  </div>
</div>

      <div class="step screensteps-section screensteps-depth-1" id="open_inbox" data-step-uuid="cfaedcbb-1e71-4834-857c-adf0247b91a9">
